data.description: It's not perfect and that's exactly why you can buy this home with 2.59 acres and inground pool at this price!  Beautifully treed property!  Backs to large acreage that has been in same family for many years!  Enjoy the convenience of being only 3 miles from Hwy. 29 and only 8 minutes from downtown Liberty Hill.  Lots of potential (handyman special - needs updating) in this 2 story home featuring 3 bedrooms; 2 baths; 2 living areas each with fireplace; primary bedroom with sitting area or office with private access to deck overlooking pool;  metal roof; in-ground swimming pool...... situated on heavily treed 2.59 acres!   No HOA; very few restrictions; low taxes and located in the highly sought after Liberty Hill school district!  Selling "as is".
